author: sussman
msg: Big API change:  toss RA->do_checkout().  'Tis no more.
Note that 'svn export' and 'svn cp URL wc' needed to be tweaked as
well, just like 'svn checkout' did in r6029.  All three codepaths
were calling RA->do_checkout(), and now they call RA->do_update instead.
* libsvn_repos/checkout.c:  delete entire file; this implementation was
used by both ra_local and svnserve.
RA->do_checkout, call RA->do_update and manufacture a simple report.
